  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Quang Tri improves its adaptive capacity and recilience to climate chang. Local communities in Quang Tri province improves its adaptive capacity and resilience to climate change. 1.To enhance capacity of community based disaster risk management and climate change adaptation for local partners and local communities.  2.To facilitate farmerled action research in the local area including sandy land reformation, sand fill up use, droughts related to crop varieties and irrigation and salt intrusion. 3. To enhance the community resilience to climate change adaptation through livelihoods improvement.  4. To advocate the integration of climate change and disaster risks management into the social economic planning of commune and district level.</narrative>
  </description>
